TITLE: Defining DejaVu Sans Font Family in JasperReports fonts.xml
DESCRIPTION: This XML snippet defines the 'DejaVu Sans' font family within a JasperReports `fonts.xml` file. It maps the normal, bold, italic, and boldItalic styles to their respective TTF files, sets PDF encoding to 'Identity-H' and enables embedding. It also includes export mappings for HTML, suggesting fallback fonts. Locale support is commented out, implying universal applicability unless uncommented.
SOURCE: https://github.com/jaspersoft/jasperreports/blob/master/demo/samples/fonts/README.md#2025-04-22_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: xml
CODE:
```
