TITLE: Mapping Logical JVM Fonts for HTML Export in JasperReports fonts.xml
DESCRIPTION: This XML snippet within `fonts.xml` maps standard logical font names ('SansSerif', 'Serif', 'Monospaced') used in reports to specific font families (like the previously defined DejaVu fonts) for the HTML exporter. This ensures appropriate font rendering or fallback options in HTML output.
SOURCE: https://github.com/jaspersoft/jasperreports/blob/master/demo/samples/fonts/README.md#2025-04-22_snippet_5

