TITLE: Mapping Address Entity to ADDRESS Table - Hibernate XML Mapping
DESCRIPTION: Provides Hibernate XML mapping for the Address entity to the ADDRESS table, establishing fields and a set-based one-to-many relationship to Document. To be placed in src/Address.hbm.xml; requires Address.java and Document mapping/files to function properly. Used by Hibernate during ORM for query and persistence operations.
